title: Alex Jones Show - 2011 July 03 SU [sebaygo1]
description:

The Alex Jones Show
Sunday, 03 July 2011


[sebaygo1]


The 2 hour Sunday show is typically a review of the past week's news and a look forward to the coming week's events.

The Infowars web site describes today's broadcast as follows.

On this July 3rd encore presentation of the Alex Jones Show, Alex talks with Texas Congressman Ron Paul, trends researcher and author Gerald Celente, and author and researcher Webster Tarpley who is on a fact-find mission to Libya as the U.S. and NATO continue to bombard that country. 

Also featured is Alex's keynote speech at this year's Talkers New Media Conference in New York City.
